  FAMOUS PEOPLE
============================================================

Name:          Charles Darwin
Lived:         1809 - 1882
Nationality:   English
Field:         Biology
Known For:     Evolution by Natural Selection
Contribution:  On the Origin of Species; explained diversity of life on Earth
Quote:         "It is not the strongest that survives, but the most adaptable."

Name:          Ada Lovelace
Lived:         1815 - 1852
Nationality:   English
Field:         Computing
Known For:     First computer algorithm
Contribution:  Wrote first algorithm for Babbage's machine; recognized computing potential
Quote:         "The Analytical Engine weaves algebraic patterns."

Name:          Leonardo da Vinci
Lived:         1452 - 1519
Nationality:   Italian
Field:         Art/Science
Known For:     Mona Lisa, anatomy
Contribution:  Renaissance polymath; Mona Lisa; anatomical drawings; flying machine designs
Quote:         "Learning never exhausts the mind."

