Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     11 years
Weight:       30 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         80% hunting success rate; votes on hunts by sneezing democratically

Name:         Monarch Butterfly
Scientific:   Danaus plexippus
Class:        Insecta
Habitat:      Meadows
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     0.25 years
Weight:       0.0005 kg
Status:       Endangered
